                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Rockhill</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-04-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 23, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Reports that an edict provides for the removal of the governor of Kiangsi from
                    office and the punishment of the provincial judge and treasurer on account of
                    the riot at Nan-ch’ang.)</p>
            </div>
